item.title: By: Airport Shuttle SA
item.dc:creator: Airport Shuttle SA
item.description:
This is one of my favorites events in South Africa, i had such great time, you feel free like a bird, you can do what ever you want! (well kind of...lol).
Thanks for posting those awesome pictures, brings back good memories.
See you again on April 27, 2015, can't wait!
Awesome blog btw.
Eric Cohen.
